## User Actions

### Edit # (Count)
- Click the number input → type new value → press Enter or click away
- Green flash = saved successfully
- Red flash = save failed
- If value didn't change, no update is sent (no-change guard)

### Toggle Done
- Click the checkbox to mark/unmark as done
- Orange filled = done, empty = not done

### Skip Row
- Click the X button on any row to hide it
- Skipped rows are excluded from Total # and Payment calculations
- Toggle "Show Hidden" (eye icon in Skip column header) to see skipped rows
- Skipped rows count shown as "(N)" next to the eye icon

### Add Row
- Click "+ Add Row" on any week separator
- Select date and job type from dropdowns
- Click "Add" to insert, "Cancel" to close
- Available job types: VVIP, Links Input, New Items, VVIP SG, New Items SG

### Generate New Cycle
- Click the "+ New Cycle" card
- Auto-generates all weekday rows for the next 28-day cycle
- Uses the fixed weekly schedule (see below)

