## Audit Trail (History Logs)

All changes are logged to the `history_logs` table. Users can see the last change by hovering on specific cells.

| Hover on | Shows | Log Action |
|----------|-------|------------|
| **Date** column | Who manually added this row and when | `create_row` |
| **#** column | Who changed the count, old → new value | `update_count` |
| **Done** checkbox | Who toggled done, Done/Not Done | `update_done` |
| **"skipped"** label (in Show Hidden mode) | Who skipped the row, Visible → Skipped | `update_hidden` |

### History Popover
- Appears on hover after 400ms delay
- Shows: "By [email]", "At DD/MM/YYYY, HH:MM:SS", Old/New values
- For create_row: Shows "Created" title + job type
- Fetches from `GET /api/job-cycle/:id` (last 20 entries)

### No-Change Guard
If a user edits # to the same value (e.g., 200 → 200), no update or log is created. The API returns `{ success: true, noChange: true }`.

