## Database Schema

**Table**: `AllBots.job_cycle_ca`

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | INT AUTO_INCREMENT | Primary key |
| cycle | INT NOT NULL | Cycle number (17, 18, 19, ...) |
| job_date | DATE NOT NULL | The date of the job |
| job_type | VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL | Job type name (VVIP, Links Input, etc.) |
| count | INT DEFAULT 0 | Number of items processed |
| done | TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0 | 1 = done, 0 = not done |
| hidden | TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0 | 1 = skipped/hidden, 0 = visible |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Auto-updates on any change |

**Unique Key**: `uq_row (cycle, job_date, job_type)` — prevents duplicate rows

**Audit Logs**: Stored in `AllBots.history_logs` with `model_name = 'job_cycle_ca'`

